<span id="freeTextContainer7034123186215247910">I found the novel fascinating with simple but captivating writing. Simple story but deep subtext about colonialism and class and gender and race although completely from the point of view of two British white womyn 50 years apart. I guess it’s an early version of desperate housewives; the British colonists version. </span>

