          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780860074144" href="/book/show/2702984-heat-and-dust">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/41741555-ana?shelf=adult">adult</a>, 
